  %p.intro
    Please review your order and click 'Update cart' if there is anything which needs changing. Then click 'Confirm' when you are satisfied to 
    -if uses_paypal?
      go to PayPal and 
    complete the order.
  =render :partial => 'carts/form', :locals => {:cart => cart}
  %p
    =link_to 'Confirm', orders_path, :method => :post, :class => 'bttn_l'
